int32_t CLI_MMWaveExtensionHandler ( int32_t  argc,
char *  argv[] 
)

Description
This is the mmWave extension handler which executes mmWave extension commands. This is invoked by the main CLI wrapper only if the extension was enabled.

Parameters
[in]argcNumber of detected arguments
[in]argvDetected arguments
Return values
0- Matching mmWave extension command found
-1- No Matching mmWave extension command
